@node Main "Pathos - Documentation"

                              'Pathos' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Pathos' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} based on the well known
'sliding-tiles' concept. The idea is to move tiles that have parts
of 'paths' on them, so they create a path between the entry,
located at the top, to the exit, which is located at the bottom of
the game board.

  Pathos keeps in memory the number of tiles that are used to
create the longest and shortest path since the game was run...  

  Have fun!

